data.description: Luxury living with a farmhouse flair!  Set on a fenced-in 3/4-acre cul-de-sac lot, this stunning custom home with a 3-car garage has it all!  Featuring main-level living with the primary bedroom and two secondary bedrooms on the first level, office, dining room, gourmet eat-in kitchen featuring gas cooktop, quartz countertops, custom cabinets, large island with granite countertop, 12' ceilings in family room, screened in porch, plantation shutters through-out, extensive trim, designer walls and ceilings, custom built-ins and site finished hardwoods.  Large bonus, fourth bedroom, full bath and tons of walk-in storage complete the second level.  This is one you don't want to miss!!
